<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>第一名考了多少分？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200826/7ed20a092d74405a96a67c9498397d5b.png" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">图片来源于网络</span></img></p>
